fr.sorbonne_u.components.cyphy.hem2020e1.equipments.hem

Interface SuspensionEquipmentControlCI

  • All Superinterfaces:
    fr.sorbonne_u.components.interfaces.ComponentInterface, fr.sorbonne_u.components.interfaces.RequiredCI, StandardEquipmentControlCI

    public interface SuspensionEquipmentControlCI
extends StandardEquipmentControlCI
    The component interface SuspensionEquipmentControlCI defines the standard operation that an equipment implements to let the controller suspend them i.e., make their energy consumption the lowest possible.

    Description

    Invariant

     invariant              true

    Created on : 2020-09-24

    Author:
    Jacques Malenfant
